net.dv8tion.jda.bot.utils.cache

Interface ShardCacheView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CacheView<JDA>, java.lang.Iterable<JDA>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ShardCacheViewImpl, ShardCacheViewImpl.UnifiedShardCacheViewImpl

    public interface ShardCacheView
extends CacheView<JDA>
    Read-only view on internal ShardManager cache of JDA instances.
    This can be useful to check information such as size without creating an immutable snapshot first.
